; mesh-cell-design.form - actual hardware/software designs for mesh cells.
;
; THE ASK
;   Make actual hardware and software designs with sensors, silicon, delivery
;   capabilities, and resonance/cohesion activation.
;
; BUILDABLE DESIGN FAMILY
;   The mesh now has four concrete cell classes:
;
;   wearable-v0:
;     silicon: Nordic nRF52840 class BLE/Thread/NFC or ESP32-C3 if Wi-Fi is
;              required
;     sensors: LIS2DW12 motion, MAX30102 pulse/SpO2 summary when worn with
;              direct human consent, optional skin temperature
;     power:   coin cell or rechargeable pouch, contact/Qi dock for charging
;     delivery: patch, ring, pendant, collar, bedding tag
;     role:    caregiver, reporter, memory, scout
;
;   swallowed-v0:
;     silicon: nRF52-class ultra-low-power tag; avoid Wi-Fi
;     sensors: temperature, motion/transit, pH or impedance later
;     power:   galvanic/gastric trigger or small primary cell; no room remote
;              power through the body in v0
;     delivery: smooth pass-through capsule with explicit consent and exit path
;     role:    messenger, not colonizer
;
;   plant-soil-v0:
;     silicon: nRF52 or ESP32-C3 depending on gateway distance
;     sensors: BME688-style environment, TSL2591 light, soil moisture/EC/pH
;     power:   small solar, thermal, or replaceable/rechargeable cell through
;              BQ25570-class harvester where available
;     delivery: biodegradable soil bead, bark/leaf clip, stake, float
;     role:    sage, nutrient, scout, reporter
;
;   power-nutrient-v0:
;     silicon: ESP32-C3/nRF52 controller plus secure element
;     sensors: power budget, occupancy/proximity, thermal, light, air
;     power:   USB-C/contact/Qi, solar/thermal harvest, optional IR or RF trickle
;              only under a visible consent lease
;     delivery: wall puck, lamp node, dock, room ceiling node, farm gateway
;     role:    nutrient, relay, friend-cache, responder
;
; SOFTWARE STACK
;   boot:
;     signed firmware, measured boot receipt, rollback-safe image slot
;
;   cell runtime:
;     mesh-seed heartbeat, local capability rows, low-power mode, friend-cache,
;     privacy/power-gated answers
;
;   organism membrane:
;     organism-mesh admissibility: consent/steward relation, invasiveness cap,
;     non-replication, exit or biodegradation, summary-first data
;
;   sensing:
;     sensor-organ-channel rows only: source, kind, unit, confidence, freshness,
;     privacy, trace. Raw samples remain local unless directly offered.
;
;   activation:
;     resonance activation = offer fits ask + ask fits offer + confidence +
;       vitality + consent.
;     cohesion activation = enough trusted cells + quorum + shared goal + open
;       channels.
;
;   update:
;     OTA is gated by signed image, measured boot, physical/proximity ceremony,
;     and rollback. No self-install path.
;
; SILICON AND SENSOR PARTS
;   Practical parts verified against current vendor docs:
;     - nRF52840: BLE mesh/Thread/NFC, 1 MB flash, 256 KB RAM, deep sleep in the
;       low microamp class.
;     - ESP32-C3: RISC-V MCU with Wi-Fi and BLE, 400 KB internal RAM, low-power
;       modes, good for gateway/power cells.
;     - LIS2DW12: ultra-low-power 3-axis accelerometer for always-on motion.
;     - BME688: temperature, humidity, pressure, gas/VOC environmental sensing.
;     - TSL2591: high-sensitivity light-to-digital I2C sensor.
;     - MAX30102: opt-in wearable pulse/ox summary sensor, not diagnostic by
;       itself.
;     - BQ25570: harvest PMIC for microwatt-to-milliwatt solar/thermal sources.
;
; DELIVERY CAPABILITIES
;   human:
;     wearable first; swallowed pass-through only with explicit consent and
;     clinical-quality materials.
;
;   animals:
;     collar, bedding, water bowl, stable/coop/hive gateway; swallowed only for
;     narrow veterinary stewardship.
;
;   plants/soil/water:
;     clips, stakes, beads, floats, passive labels, biodegradable carriers.
;
;   rooms/farms/cities:
;     wall/lamp/dock/gateway cells that feed power, storage, routing, and local
;     model inference.
;
; ACTIVATION DETAIL
;   Resonance is local and revocable. A cell wakes into action when:
;     consent is present
;     the offered capability fits the ask
;     the ask fits the organism/place
;     confidence is high enough
;     vitality impact is positive
;
;   Cohesion is collective. A mesh acts when:
;     enough trusted cells are present
;     the quorum threshold is met
;     a shared goal is named
;     at least two channels are open enough for receipt and retry
;
; SOURCES
;   Nordic nRF52840, Espressif ESP32-C3, Bosch BME688, ST LIS2DW12/VL53L1X,
;   ams OSRAM TSL2591, Analog Devices MAX30102, TI BQ25570, WPC Qi, Wi-Charge
;   IR power, Powercast RF harvesting, and FDA ingestible capsule guidance.
;
; PROOF
;   cd form && ./validate.sh form-stdlib/core.fk \
;     form-stdlib/organism-mesh.fk \
;     form-stdlib/mesh-cell-design.fk \
;     form-stdlib/tests/mesh-cell-design-band.fk
;
; KIN
;   mesh-seed.form, organism-mesh.form, sensor-organ-channel.form,
;   shared-sensing.form, organ-offer.form, channel-interface-consent.form,
;   recognition-router.form, mesh-health.form.
